1980. More or less around 1980. Well, then after he 
married, the second time he returned to Mexico.

23:40.737 --> 23:41.958
Yes, and he had this child. And he naturally, he 
adored him because he was, well, for one thing, We

23:51.605 --> 23:52.686
two were married. My sister and I were married. And 
